      <title>特朗普拒绝与哈里斯辩论，称哈里斯在民调中领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-pushes-back-on-debate-with-harris-saying-he-s-up-in-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普拒绝与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯辩论的压力，称他在民意调查中领先，选民已经知道他和他的民主党对手在这些问题上的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-pushes-back-on-debate-with-harris-saying-he-s-up-in-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 12:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙力推私营部门在下届内阁中拥有代表权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dimon-pushes-for-private-sector-representation-in-next-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司首席执行官杰米戴蒙表示，随着国内和地缘政治问题日益突出，下一任美国总统必须努力让“严重分裂”的国家团结起来，并表示商界应该在内阁中拥有代表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dimon-pushes-for-private-sector-representation-in-next-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 11:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦拘留维权人士 警告民众不要抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/zimbabwe-warns-against-protests-as-it-detains-rights-activists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦本月晚些时候将就任南部非洲经济集团主席国，在此次区域峰会之前，津巴布韦警告反对派不要举行抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/zimbabwe-warns-against-protests-as-it-detains-rights-activists</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:55:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>詹里克称保守党尽管惨败但仍能赢得下届英国大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/jenrick-to-say-tories-can-win-next-uk-election-despite-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正在争夺保守党领袖职位的罗伯特·詹里克 (Robert Jenrick) 将于周五向党员表示，保守党能够从上个月大选中的历史性失败中恢复过来，赢得下届英国大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/jenrick-to-say-tories-can-win-next-uk-election-despite-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议活动引发对改革的担忧，尼日利亚债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nigeria-s-deadly-cost-of-living-protests-spook-bond-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心全国各地的生活成本抗议活动可能会破坏政府的经济改革计划，尼日利亚的主权风险溢价飙升至八个月高点，其美元债券是周五表现最差的新兴市场资产之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nigeria-s-deadly-cost-of-living-protests-spook-bond-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里叛军称在冲突中杀死了 131 名瓦格纳和军队士兵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/mali-rebels-say-they-killed-131-wagner-army-soldiers-in-clashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里叛军组织称，上个月在与西非国家俄罗斯雇佣军支持的军队的战斗中，该组织杀死了数十名士兵和外国战士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/mali-rebels-say-they-killed-131-wagner-army-soldiers-in-clashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚抗议者高呼“我们饿了”，13 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/-we-are-hungry-chant-nigerian-protesters-as-13-people-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚安全部队对非洲人口第一大国抗议高生活成本的抗议活动进行镇压，造成至少 13 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/-we-are-hungry-chant-nigerian-protesters-as-13-people-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其因哈马斯“审查”争端封锁 Instagram</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的一名高级助手批评社交媒体平台“审查”与哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚之死相关的帖子后，土耳其互联网监管机构封锁了 Instagram 的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国支持过渡，委内瑞拉反对派呼吁抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/venezuela-opposition-s-machado-says-she-s-in-hiding-wsj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被禁的反对派领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多呼吁委内瑞拉全国各地举行抗议活动，捍卫其政党认为的合法选举胜利，而总统乔·拜登的高级外交官表示，美国支持权力过渡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/venezuela-opposition-s-machado-says-she-s-in-hiding-wsj</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
